Sentencas: Ag-network was successfully deposited by VA-EP (vacuum assisted electroless plating) method on Pr1.6Sr0.4NiO4 YSZ cathode to form (1-x) wt% Pr1.6Sr0.4NiO4
Titulo: Investigations on Pr1.6Sr0.4NiO4-YSZ-Ag composite cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: XRD results suggested that there was a good chemical stability between Pr1.6Sr0.4NiO4 and YSZ at temperatures below 1050 degrees C. PY20-Ag cathode exhibited higher exchange current density, lower overpotential and ASR (Area Specific Resistance) than PY20 cathode.
Titulo: Investigations on Pr1.6Sr0.4NiO4-YSZ-Ag composite cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: At 650 degrees C, the ASR of PY20-Ag cathode was 2.5 Omega cm(2), which was only about 42% of that of PY20, 5.9 Omega cm(2).
Titulo: Investigations on Pr1.6Sr0.4NiO4-YSZ-Ag composite cathode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: PY20-Ag can be a promising candidate for SOFC cathode.
